  "original_title": "''\u0d85\u0db4\u0ddd \u0daf\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0dca\u0d9a\u0dcf...\u0daf\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0dca\u0d9a\u0dcf. \u0dbd\u0ddc\u0d9a\u0dca\u0d9a\u0dcf \u0d9c\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad \u0dc3\u0dd0\u0db4 \u0dc4\u0ddc\u0db3\u0da7\u0db8 \u0daf\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0dca\u0d9a\u0dcf.''",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"I saw...I saw. I saw the pleasure that the boss took very well.''",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A large number of people came today (July 11) to see the President's House, the Temple House and the President's Secretariat, which were seized by the militants.",
        "Many of them said that they were happy to see these mansions which they had never seen before. Although unable to come to Colombo, a group of people who visited the mansions through the media also expressed their views to the BBC.",
        "\"I saw the pleasures that the boss took. We suffer in the queues.\" \"Life does not get to see. One came with children.'' etc. they mentioned."
      ],
